_sText:
Regular-sized Fight Yard map with a waterpit in the middle and a sniper tower on each side.
The weapons are:
M4A1
AK-47
Deagle
Para
Awp
Scout
M3 Shotgun
HE
Flashbang
MP5

Thanks to Terkaal for testing every single ver!

-UPDATE-

fy_waterpit -> fy_waterpit_final changes:
Texture errors fixed.
Added new decals and interactive lights.
MP5's can now be found in any of the two towers.
Fixed the skybox, you can no longer jump out of the map.
